# Technical Specification Sheet: Sapphire-Hybrid Boiler v1.0

## 1. Core Pressure Tube 
* **Material:** Monocrystalline Sapphire (Al₂O₃) - Optical Grade.
* **Melting Point:** 2040°C.
* **Working Pressure:** Nominal 250 Bar / Peak 350 Bar (Supercritical Phase).
* **Safety Factor:** 4:1 (Based on Modulus of Rupture).
* **Dimensions:** Inner Diameter: 20mm | Wall Thickness: 5mm.
* **Surface Finish:** Chemically polished (Inner/Outer) to prevent scaling.

## 2. Optical Interface & Laser Injection 
* **Configuration:** Hemispherical Pressure Domes (Sapphire).
* **Primary Input:** Concentrated Solar Flux.
* **Laser Source:** Nd:YAG Laser (1.064 µm wavelength).
* **Optical Coating:** High-temperature Hafnium Oxide (HfO₂) Anti-Reflective coating.
* **Function:** Immediate volumetric heating of water/steam to supercritical states.

## 3. Thermal Storage Unit 
* **PCM Material:** Eutectic Aluminum-Silicon Alloy (Al-Si12).
* **Phase Change Temperature:** 577°C (Isothermal storage).
* **Latent Heat of Fusion:** ~560 kJ/kg.
* **Thermal Conductivity:** 160 W/m·K (High-speed heat distribution).
* **Storage Capacity:** Designed for 48-hour continuous discharge.

## 4. Structural Housing & Insulation 
* **Outer Shell:** Cast Chromium-Molybdenum Steel (Grade P91).
* **Internal Lining:** Titanium Nitride (TiN) chemical barrier to prevent Al-Si corrosion.
* **Insulation Layer:** High-density Alumina-Silica fiber blanket.
* **Heat Recovery:** Integrated Regenerative Counter-flow Water Jacket.

## 5. Performance Metrics 
* **Steam Exit Temperature:** 550°C - 600°C.
* **Thermal Efficiency:** >95% (System-wide).
* **Response Time:** Near-instantaneous (Laser-activated).
